fields.name: Data
fields.description: Base-64 encoded pfx certificate. Only applicable in PUT Request.

fields.name: KeyVaultSecretId
fields.description: Secret Id of (base-64 encoded unencrypted pfx) 'Secret' or 'Certificate' object stored in KeyVault.

fields.name: Password
fields.description: Password for the pfx file specified in data. Only applicable in PUT request.

fields.name: PublicCertData
fields.description: Base-64 encoded Public cert data corresponding to pfx specified in data. Only applicable in GET request.
